data.description: Motivated seller, and already $15k+ under appraised value!  Stop your search, and welcome this northwest single story house to market!  Your new home features three bedrooms/two bathrooms, a two car garage, and a beautiful backyard!  Pull up to curb appeal, and enter to an inviting open floor plan.  The main living area flows into the dining room and kitchen.  Your new kitchen includes a spacious pantry, cabinet space, an island, and all major appliances included!  Head down the hallway to all bedrooms, including the primary bed/bathrooms.  Fit for a king/queen, these rooms include a walk-in closet, ceiling fans, and double sinks!  Your private lot has a covered patio, mature landscaping, real grass, and plenty more room for your imagination!  Solar screens throughout home!  Low maintenance HOA!  Conveniently located to all highway, shopping, and entertainment needs.. Come on by while this one lasts!
